commentary: Mohammad Saifuddin to Guptill, OUT taken brilliantly at long-on and Guptill won't be the first from his country to get three hundreds in a bilateral series. It was full on off, Guptill picked him up down the ground, perhaps meant to go slightly straighter, but the fielder judged it beautifully, first taking it and then as he overbalanced, had the presence of mind to toss it up back into play and catch it again while he was in the air, before coming back into playing area
